reviewText: This was part of a collection for our son.  The condition was acceptable, and was shipped in a timely fashion.  It is a great way to add to collections, without having to spend a lot of money.

Contains "Yosemite Remedy" (from ep. 12), "Kenya Be My Friend?" (from ep. 2) and "Rafiki Fables: The Sky Is Calling" (from ep. 12).

This is the fourth volume in the series. Highly recommend this for the collectors and die hard Disney and Lion King fans.
